title: The commencement of the treaty between the king's Majesty, and the Commissioners of Parliament at Newport.
author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1625-1649 : Charles I)
notes: Dated at end: Newport in Insula vectis. Septemb. 16. 1648.
Includes: A prayer, drawne by his Majesties speciall direction and dictates, for a blessing on the treaty at Newport.
